snippet.title: Obscure GBC Gaming 3 - Hello Kitty to Dear Daniel no Dream Adventure
snippet.description: Hello Kitty to Dear Daniel no Dream Adventure - is platform game with Hello Kitty for GBC. It is sequel to the Hello Kitty no Sweet Adventure: Daniel-kun ni Aitai \ Dear Daniel no Sweet Adventure - Kitty-chan wo Sagashite.
